Pipa Studios only collects information voluntarily coming from: purchase of services, registration for participation online game player connection, chat, claims a client, research, technical support or newsletter. Personal information collected may include your name, address, phone number and/or e-mail. We do not require this information to gain access to our sites, however, you can not use certain products, services, features that require registration or receive materials such as newsletters unless such information is provided.
What other types of information can be collected?
For all other activities we may ask you to provide non-personal information such as age, date of birth, marital status and sex. In addition, your web browser may transmit certain geographic information or related to your computer (data processing capacity and the game). Team Beach Bingo can use this information to generate statistics about our customers and provide such information to advertisers and/or partners, as well as use for system security.
How we use your personal information?
Your personal information will allow us to fill your requests for products or services and to alert you about new products and/or services, features or game updates, treat and track issues and notify you of promotions and events. We may use your personal information for internal marketing, profiling, or demographic purposes, so we can adapt our products and services to better meet your needs. We do this to better understand and serve our customers.
Who is collecting your information?
Your information is shared with Pipa Studios Team, its parent, affiliates and associated companies, except where specifically stated otherwise.
Be aware that advertisers or websites with links to our sites may collect personal information about you. And remember, this Privacy Policy does not apply to and can not control the activities of such other advertisers or web sites.
